hackathon-description-text: This February brings us the third StrathHACK event! Again we have the privilage of hosting in the Architecture Building within the University of Strathclyde, right in the heart of Glasgow City Centre.
hackathon-eligibility: Attendees should be aged 18 or over and be registered European Students

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: £50 In cash for each team member (Max 5)

hackathon-location-google-maps: https://maps.google.com/?q=131 Rottenrow E, Glasgow G4 0NG, UK

hackathon-judging-criteria.judging-criterion: The judges will determine best in challenge

hackathon-description-header: Build something Awesome, Shape the future
